Only add catch blocks when the component needs behavior `ErrorBoundary` can't provide â€” typically **retries** or **timeout-specific messages**. Even then, only catch what you need:

```csharp
// Catch only external cancellation (timeouts) â€” everything else flows to ErrorBoundary
